The first¬†<em>Sharing Power</em> episode of our second season was with Ari Gass and Daniel Park about their collaboration in Obvious Agency:
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/6JcRU1sHv1LzXXIwFtDcRq">Listen on Spotify</a></h2>
